propertyDescriptor.name: File Filter Regex
propertyDescriptor.description: Provides a Java Regular Expression for filtering Filenames; if a filter is supplied, only files whose names match that Regular Expression will be fetched

propertyDescriptor.name: Hostname
propertyDescriptor.description: The fully qualified hostname or IP address of the remote system

propertyDescriptor.name: Password
propertyDescriptor.description: Password for the user account

propertyDescriptor.name: Remote Path
propertyDescriptor.description: The path on the remote system from which to pull or push files

propertyDescriptor.name: Search Recursively
propertyDescriptor.description: If true, will pull files from arbitrarily nested subdirectories; otherwise, will not traverse subdirectories

propertyDescriptor.name: Username
propertyDescriptor.description: Username

propertyDescriptor.name: Completion Strategy
propertyDescriptor.description: Specifies what to do with the original file on the server once it has been pulled into NiFi. If the Completion Strategy fails, a warning will be logged but the data will still be transferred.

allowableValues.description: Move the file to the directory specified by the <Move Destination Directory> property
Deletes the original file from the remote system
